data.text:
2015-2016: 14th at Falcon Open…second in junior’s at Nick Toth Open…tied for third in senior mixed epee and first in junior epee at the Amarillo Open…66th in epee at NAC in Richmond VA.

2014-15: In 2014, tied for third in both the senior men’s epee and (U20) championships at the Parker Kickoff Open … eighth place in senior mixed epee and 10th in (U20) at the Amarillo Open … placed 56th overall in Div. I epee at the Div. I NAC in Portland … 70th overall in junior’s at the NAC in Louisville … 6-9 at the Brandeis Invitational … 34th in Div. I and 49th in juniors at the Div. I NAC in Salt Lake.

Before the Academy: Competed at LAIFC (Los Angeles International Fencing Center) and BBFC (Battle-Born Fencing Club) … coached by Vadim Diambekov, Kay Kim, Gago Demirchian / Jacques Lacour, Yves Auriol.
